mysql> SELECT
    ->
    -> CONCAT(title, ' - ', released_year) as 'summary'
    ->
    -> FROM books
    ->
    -> ORDER BY released_year DESC LIMIT 3
    -> ;
+-----------------------------+
| summary                     |
+-----------------------------+
| Lincoln In The Bardo - 2017 |
| Lincoln In The Bardo - 2017 |
| Norse Mythology - 2016      |
